Life in a flood zone: how to prepare for evacuation and what things to pack in advance?
- Take a flashlight and batteries for it, warm clothes and food that does not spoil - canned food, preferably with a ring so that you can open the jar with your hands, bread, cookies, chocolate;
Show more
— We put a penknife or knife in a case;
— A container with a lid for food products - in case of a flood, pack documents in it;
— A large piece of polyethylene might come in handy if you suddenly have to sit on the roof in the rain. Wrap a blanket in it;
- And be sure to take a coil of thick rope - it will help if you need to wait out the night on the roof.
